name: @sima-land/ui-quarks
description: Sima-land design system icons as a React components
author: www.sima-land.ru team

scripts.build: npm run build:before && npm run build:main && npm run build:esm && npm run build:cjs && npm run build:types && npm run build:after
scripts.sync:exports: node --import=tsimp/import scripts/emit-exports.mts && npm pkg set --json exports="$(cat ./temp/exports.json)" && rm -rf temp/exports.json
scripts.dist: npm run build && npm run sync:exports
